ygData.messageBody:
>VERY cute, if you like 'em tall & Texan!!!

Okay, several of my email lists suddenly grew talkative today, so I am
little confused about all the emails I have this evening. Who else here
is Texan? (raised in west texas, myself, in the midland area, but i
spent about 8 years in austin recently too)

Also, Nameless Love is very near to creation on The Nameless server. We
have 9 of our necessary 10 people located. Anyone else interested in
helping us start the new guild?

Here's the current temporary (still-in-development) site:

http://www.visi.com/~dsundeen/guild/nl.html

Drop me an email if you'd like to help us out. I intend to get the
guild registered before the end of the month. :) We could sure use an
extra one or two people to join too, though, in case we have problems
arranging a time that all of us can be online.
